  "content": "According to reports, President Joe Biden attended a birthday party in Manhattan in November 2020 despite his own administration's guidelines advising against large gatherings due to the ongoing pandemic. This incident drew criticism from various media outlets and political opponents who pointed out the apparent contradiction between the President's public health messaging and his private actions.\n\nSource: https://halifax.citynews.ca/2024/09/24/joe--video-reveals-he-attended-parties-during-pandemic/",
